Pre-Game Insights: Angola qualified for the knockout stage for the first time in AFCON history.
Namibia stunned Tunisia by beating one of the favourites but lost to South Africa and drew with Mali.
Dala Gelson and Mabululu have scored two goals each together.
Deon Hotto has been one of the biggest scorers for Namibia.
Angola are unbeaten in the last eight matches.
Namibia have failed to score in the last two matches.
Angola head into the round of 16 as unbeaten.
Namibia have a fully fit squad to select from.
Angola's predicted lineup includes Neblu, Afonso, Gasper, Quinito, Carneiro, Fredy, Show, Gilberto, Zini, Gelson, and Mabululu.
Namibia's predicted lineup includes Kazapua, Kamberipa, Amutenya, Haukonho, Hanamub, Petrus, Muzeu, Tijiueza, Katua, Hotto, and Shalulile.
